    • OnActionModPartSave

      public void OnActionModPartSave(javafx.event.ActionEvent event) throws IOException
      LOGICAL ERROR: When a part is selected, then modified and saved, when trying to modify again, the radio button switches from InHouse to Outsourced even when originally InHouse was saved. To fix this issue, I used two else if statement to check if the boolean for the radio buttons are true or false, which will then update the part depending on which radio button is selected. This allows the input to be updated and saved
      Throws:
      IOException
